Pho:
- Beef bones (for broth)
- Beef cuts (brisket, flank, etc.)
- Rice noodles
- Onion
- Ginger
- Star anise
- Cinnamon stick
- Cloves
- Cardamom pods
- Fish sauce
- Rock sugar
- Fresh herbs (Thai basil, cilantro, mint)
- Bean sprouts
- Lime wedges
- Chili peppers (sliced)
- Hoisin sauce and sriracha (for serving)
- Optional: Beef meatballs, tendon, tripe (for variations)
